title: To provide for conveyances of certain lands in Alaska to Chickaloon-Moose Creek Native Association, Inc., Ninilchik Native Association, Inc., Seldovia Native Association, Inc., Tyonek Native Corporation, and Knikatnu, Inc. under the Alaska Native Claims Settlement Act.
content: Amends Federal law to provide for conveyance of certain Alaskan lands under the Alaska Native Claims Settlement Act to: (1) Chickaloon-Moose Creek Native Association, Inc., (2) Knikatnu, Inc., (3) Ninilchik Native Association, Inc., (4) Seldovia Native Association, Inc., and (5) Tyonek Native Corporation.
